是政府豁免海員，機組人員檢疫。他說相信政府有認真聽專家意見，但做決定時可能有其他考慮。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">據了解，上一次開會是7月初，即疫情最嚴峻的這兩個多星期沒有再開專家組會議。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-cn.facebook.com/icablenews/posts/1514102325448497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-cn.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fposts%2F1514102325448497&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6ZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=6c4e7d21\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-cn.facebook.com/icablenews/posts/1514102325448497</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n專家 係咪配票專家計唔掂條數呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"有會議紀錄<br />\n怕有真專家提反對意見<br />\n如果唔理強推<br />\n事後查番就有責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652ea272fed37c5e22c653c5d5e3f28dd672002b","tid":2130093,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"諮詢專家意見 唔等於 諮詢<span class=\"red\">抗疫</span>專家<br />\n專家可能係西環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d05a6bb6d98912e4bbf6463c876463ff2960754","tid":2130093,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41aaa1c2c9595d7cc20b73fc6c608d1b74e199b6","tid":2130093,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T04:53:36.000Z","msg":"搵左高永民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"九成。"},{"pid":"d8f9419433f990fa2470646f8c2e4b1b53045c50","tid":2130093,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13b2b6e04785682b5e2f41340d72b4832e4fcae1","tid":2130093,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":